Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.64,0:00:21.44,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找尋著看不見的明天 著急地用手觸摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.56,0:00:25.95,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.10,0:00:38.55,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來是沒有出口的迷宮 就像需要解謎的拼圖一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.16,0:00:49.76,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有奇蹟出現  夢想也將成為勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.00,0:00:54.94,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.05,0:00:57.86,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你的憧憬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.01,0:01:00.36,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  因為那份思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.51,0:01:03.65,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我了無形的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.93,0:01:09.77,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像稍微感受到了迷惘和煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.77,0:01:11.33,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論在什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.48,0:01:14.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.45,0:01:23.63,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  對你的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.66,0:01:28.59,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.13,0:22:23.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在心中綻放的玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.55,0:22:30.23,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗中燃盡  僅是一束火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.56,0:22:38.91,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在滿是隔閡的街上 如遊戲般的迷失自我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.04,0:22:43.19,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以小丑的心情躊躇著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.03,0:22:51.50,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要踐踏悲傷的殘片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.62,0:22:55.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人在未來中戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.42,0:23:04.02,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以解開今晚的謎底仍然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.26,0:23:08.52,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up！真面目  Hurry up！回到從前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.84,0:23:16.06,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is passion 兩個人的手中充滿的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.18,0:23:22.99,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入黑暗之中   想緊緊擁抱住陽光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.44,0:23:28.56,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在迷宮中相互Kiss
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.69,0:23:37.59,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁向樂園  僅差一道門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.50,0:00:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著時代的演進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.20,0:00:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困難的案件也與日俱增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.70,0:00:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的故事發生在企業家的別墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.80,0:00:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吊燈的死角出現了可疑的黑影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.00,0:00:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.90,0:00:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.90,0:00:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.30,0:00:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.60,0:01:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,企業家千金殺人事件(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.63,0:01:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.01,0:01:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,24歲生日快樂 麗花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.91,0:01:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.81,0:01:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天為了慶祝小女生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.02,0:02:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能請各位大老遠地到山中來為她祝賀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人真的是非常感激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.22,0:02:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也要煩請諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.02,0:02:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠多多的支持我們四井集團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.23,0:02:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吃那麼多東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.00,0:02:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難看死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.60,0:02:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.90,0:02:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個也快點吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.70,0:02:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的料理可不是隨時都吃得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.81,0:02:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高級名酒果然是不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.91,0:02:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 在大家盡情歡談之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.10,0:02:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想向大家介紹一位今天的特別來賓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.81,0:02:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利小五郎大師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.42,0:02:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個麻煩幫我包起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把它帶回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.72,0:02:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下來就太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.72,0:02:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.03,0:02:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是那位出名的毛利小五郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.70,0:02:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.10,0:02:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.60,0:02:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在不久之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他幫了小女一個大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.90,0:02:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.00,0:02:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幫了她什麼忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.11,0:03:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是一件大案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.21,0:03:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大案子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.91,0:03:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都聽說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.20,0:03:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.00,0:03:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以把麗花小姐的愛犬巴布魯找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.20,0:03:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常不容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.90,0:03:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.62,0:03:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.10,0:03:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做一枝隆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.70,0:03:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能夠見到鼎鼎大名的名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.60,0:03:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太榮幸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.60,0:03:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您太客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.40,0:03:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想只要您用那銳利的眼神一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的犯人都當場投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.41,0:03:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上招認他們的罪狀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.71,0:03:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是麗花小姐委託的名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.01,0:03:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們三個有完沒完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.51,0:03:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道在那裡逢迎拍馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.22,0:03:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.02,0:03:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們只是想拍麗花小姐的馬屁而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.12,0:03:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.40,0:03:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個你們所說的名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.23,0:03:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就是一個中年的大叔而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.93,0:03:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.80,0:03:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.20,0:03:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一針見血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.20,0:03:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一定這樣想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.90,0:03:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.50,0:04:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來一直期待今天的會面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.10,0:04:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和我想像的差太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.61,0:04:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們竟然都這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.41,0:04:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你們這些小夥子就是不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.01,0:04:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不知道厲害的老鷹都是把爪子藏起來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.22,0:04:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他裝出一副窩囊相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.72,0:04:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了要解除對方的戒心而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.82,0:04:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是名偵探常用的策略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.02,0:04:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的沒錯吧 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.60,0:04:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,策略啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.40,0:04:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實麗花小姐早就看破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐她真是太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不但人長得漂亮還挺有眼光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.71,0:04:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道到底什麼人能夠成功奪取她的芳心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.71,0:04:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不知道是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.21,0:04:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過一定是個幸運的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.31,0:04:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他只要跟麗花結婚的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.62,0:04:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是四井集團下一屆的總裁候選人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廁所在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這個走廊還真是暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不把燈打開呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是儲物室啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.81,0:05:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是浴室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.81,0:05:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 廁所在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.41,0:05:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電燈打不開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.30,0:05:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.32,0:05:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想上一下廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.32,0:05:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個廁所的電燈泡壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就用對面走廊的那個廁所吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真是奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管走廊 廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.33,0:05:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是浴室裡的電燈泡全都壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.10,0:05:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我是最近才換的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.30,0:05:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.80,0:05:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才小姐坐來的那輛車已經爆胎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.01,0:05:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.41,0:05:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.21,0:05:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的法拉利送大小姐回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.61,0:05:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.21,0:05:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐我的保時捷好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.52,0:05:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是坐我的賓士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.42,0:05:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.82,0:05:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們那三輛車子好像也都爆胎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.23,0:06:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.20,0:06:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的車子竟然也一起爆胎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.60,0:06:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的車子也是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.60,0:06:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.60,0:06:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出這樣惡作劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.40,0:06:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸租來的那輛車好像沒有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.10,0:06:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆胎的車子共有6輛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.81,0:06:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.91,0:06:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好用沒事的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.21,0:06:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐六個人一起回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.11,0:06:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.91,0:06:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可是我的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.32,0:06:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要被塞在別人的車子裡面下山去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.52,0:06:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 麗花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.52,0:06:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定今天晚上要跟米嬸一起在別墅裡面過夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.02,0:06:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天叫人來接我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.33,0:06:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我留下來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.10,0:06:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也留下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.10,0:06:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.30,0:06:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也留下來好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有很多小野狼在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.30,0:06:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在也好保護小姐的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.50,0:06:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 就這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.91,0:06:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有六田先生在 我就放心多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 麗花就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.11,0:06:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上 會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.82,0:07:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗花小姐 進屋去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群做夢的笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.12,0:07:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗花小姐的對象在兩年前就已經定下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.72,0:07:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都回去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.83,0:07:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們也走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.43,0:07:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要等你的酒醒之後才能回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.60,0:07:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就留在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把以前的案子講給我們聽好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.30,0:07:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個不錯的主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.10,0:07:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看我們大家就一起玩撲克牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.01,0:07:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來快樂地度過這個晚上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.41,0:07:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能奉陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.61,0:07:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.21,0:07:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以開車送你們回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.41,0:07:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你們那輛車的鑰匙交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.82,0:07:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要回去了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.42,0:07:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.02,0:07:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來以為你也是我的老公候選者之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴你 我今天之所以到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.50,0:07:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是衝著妳老爸的面子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.20,0:07:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了我們公司的生意著想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.90,0:07:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.80,0:07:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你一點興趣也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.10,0:07:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就隨他去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.41,0:07:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.31,0:07:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們競爭的對手能少一個是一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.11,0:08:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以走了吧 偵探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.81,0:08:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 鑰匙給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.92,0:08:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.02,0:08:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想回去的話就自己回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.12,0:08:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說在前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.42,0:08:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老爸以後和你們不會有生意往來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.83,0:08:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.03,0:08:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米嬸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.90,0:08:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到2樓替我換衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.10,0:08:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 麗花小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.40,0:08:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你們全都是籠中之鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.70,0:08:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是不餵你們飼料的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.20,0:08:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們根本活不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.31,0:08:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以最好討主人的歡心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.91,0:08:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬別逞一時的意氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.42,0:08:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你們都是同一個遊艇俱樂部的成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.22,0:08:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們以前常常坐麗花小姐的遊艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.22,0:08:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到附近的小島上玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.53,0:08:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在想起來 那時候真是快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.89,0:08:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候的確很快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.30,0:08:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到兩年以前發生的那個事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.40,0:09:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事故？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.21,0:09:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些都是過去的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.01,0:09:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是約好了不再提那件事了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.81,0:09:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐換個衣服怎麼那麼慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會出了什麼事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.01,0:09:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨她去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.52,0:09:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想再忍受她大小姐的脾氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.32,0:09:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未免太慢了吧 大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.53,0:09:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米嬸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.63,0:09:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能去麗花小姐的房裡看一看怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.10,0:09:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到其他的房間去看一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.60,0:09:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.00,0:09:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.00,0:09:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我也一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.61,0:09:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.11,0:09:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼地方都不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.51,0:09:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.61,0:09:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會自己一個人走到這樹林裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.91,0:09:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在裡面迷路了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.42,0:09:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.62,0:09:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大家分頭行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.42,0:09:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起到森林裡面去找找看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.12,0:09:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.22,0:09:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個大小姐真會給人找麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.43,0:09:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.00,0:10:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗花小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.30,0:10:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.40,0:10:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到底跑到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.21,0:10:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.61,0:10:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.21,0:10:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是先回別墅好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.22,0:10:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是二階堂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.42,0:10:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方睡覺是會著涼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二階堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.50,0:10:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.70,0:10:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.50,0:10:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.60,0:10:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是溺水而死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.80,0:10:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想可能是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.71,0:10:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被人硬把臉按到噴水池裡淹死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.21,0:10:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.00,0:10:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二階堂剛才明明還活著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.81,0:11:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.11,0:11:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是在剛才被殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.58,0:11:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在這個別墅附近的什麼人幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.50,0:11:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.88,0:11:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰幹了這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.90,0:11:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是正好有一個人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們之中最可疑的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.59,0:11:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在行蹤不明的麗花大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.89,0:11:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗花小姐怎麼可能做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.90,0:11:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個現在還不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.00,0:11:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想說她也很可能被殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.60,0:11:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先報警吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.00,0:11:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.61,0:11:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等警方來之後再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.37,0:11:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話打不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.98,0:11:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 每個電話都打不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.28,0:11:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.58,0:11:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說犯人把電話線切斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.78,0:11:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.98,0:11:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用我的手機吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.88,0:11:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.89,0:11:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個地方沒有信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.49,0:11:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不出去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.10,0:11:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在只有用偵探的車子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.30,0:11:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此以外 別無他法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.50,0:11:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.39,0:11:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用那輛車去聯繫警方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.90,0:12:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才出去看過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.50,0:12:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的車子也被人家弄破輪胎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.40,0:12:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.60,0:12:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在被某個人完全的困在這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.30,0:12:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 怎麼會有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.88,0:12:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有等天亮之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.18,0:12:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人開車來接我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.88,0:12:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米嬸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.88,0:12:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思能幫我們泡杯咖啡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.90,0:12:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.79,0:12:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫妳忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.79,0:12:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三船 你要去哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.19,0:12:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.69,0:12:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.90,0:12:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我先到盥洗室那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把毛巾拿過來好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.90,0:12:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大家一定都被雨淋濕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.91,0:12:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六田叔叔 你好熟悉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.51,0:12:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個家裡的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.48,0:12:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們這群人經常在這裡聚會嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.48,0:12:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.89,0:12:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.49,0:12:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼地方都找不到砂糖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.79,0:13:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思能不能幫我看看上面的櫃子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.19,0:13:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也不在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.77,0:13:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.98,0:13:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我五年前買好後放在那裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差點給忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.48,0:13:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那包糖還能吃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.79,0:13:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前遊艇俱樂部發生了什麼事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.69,0:13:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.99,0:13:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在提這件事幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.39,0:13:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那個二階堂先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.20,0:13:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被殺之前就說過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.20,0:13:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大小姐的對象在兩年前就已經決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.70,0:13:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這跟那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.80,0:13:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.37,0:13:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子確實有必要請各位告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.88,0:13:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.78,0:13:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實那是一件不幸的悲劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.18,0:14:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是暴風雨的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.49,0:14:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前的那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.79,0:14:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這群人在附近的小島下錨之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.59,0:14:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就各自分散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.39,0:14:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到島上去玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.99,0:14:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不知道暴風雨就要來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.10,0:14:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在雷雨中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.40,0:14:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部份的人都跑到遊艇上去避難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一直在小船上的二階堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.20,0:14:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有獨自留在小島上的麗花小姐沒有回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.11,0:14:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小島每次碰到漲潮的時侯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.98,0:14:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像會沉下去一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.38,0:14:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法我們之中的一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.98,0:14:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就坐著橡皮艇去救麗花小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.38,0:14:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半天之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.48,0:14:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗花小姐跟二階堂就坐在我們的橡皮艇上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.69,0:14:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂在海面上等待救援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.49,0:14:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.89,0:14:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐橡皮艇去救他們的同伴卻找不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.19,0:14:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天之後 她的屍體就在海面上被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.70,0:14:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那個死掉的人到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是我的孫女八重子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.70,0:14:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.00,0:14:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是犧牲自己性命救回了大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.08,0:15:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這是她的希望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.68,0:15:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 我已經把咖啡泡好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.98,0:15:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.19,0:15:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.30,0:15:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得先把小姐找出來才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就先分成兩批人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.89,0:15:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把每個房間都搜一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.30,0:15:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.50,0:15:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個兇手很可能就在我們之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.20,0:15:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要注意一定不能落單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.60,0:15:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.50,0:15:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要互相監視的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.10,0:15:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有那麼危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.71,0:15:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.40,0:15:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝了咖啡以後馬上就馬上去找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.88,0:15:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候妳是怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 突然覺得好睏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.59,0:15:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了那麼多事情妳一定是累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.09,0:15:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就先躺在沙發上睡一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.99,0:15:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在旁邊看著妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.49,0:15:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.90,0:15:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到沒有 沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.70,0:15:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊呢 也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.00,0:15:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找得這麼仔細竟然找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.70,0:16:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.41,0:16:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.98,0:16:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.58,0:16:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到底到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.89,0:16:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八重子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.69,0:16:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.69,0:16:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.80,0:16:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話我們就已經把一樓都找遍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.60,0:16:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.30,0:16:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還是在樹林裡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.10,0:16:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停電嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.11,0:16:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說樓上有什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.51,0:16:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電閘在什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.78,0:16:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在廚房的對面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是什麼聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.68,0:16:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.89,0:16:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.59,0:16:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰把電源關了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.29,0:16:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是剛剛到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.29,0:16:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.50,0:17:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們開始仔仔細細的搜索這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手無處可逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.60,0:17:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才想趁著黑暗逃跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.40,0:17:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這扇窗戶就是被他弄破的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.51,0:17:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.38,0:17:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你往哪裡逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.18,0:17:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.58,0:17:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 快去阻止他們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.68,0:17:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.69,0:17:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都跑到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.39,0:17:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個樹林可是很容易迷路的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.89,0:17:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米嬸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.60,0:17:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.40,0:17:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你們臉色一下變了跑出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.70,0:17:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才追你們出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.20,0:17:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.50,0:17:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭就只有一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.38,0:17:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰 這個人是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.08,0:17:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.49,0:18:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.80,0:18:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.20,0:18:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳振作一點 小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.71,0:18:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.51,0:18:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.38,0:18:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才有人硬把我塞到水裡去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.28,0:18:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.08,0:18:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一 妳來救我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.29,0:18:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.19,0:18:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.19,0:18:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差點被妳嚇死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.60,0:18:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這就奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.10,0:18:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說發生這種事都會被嚇醒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.70,0:18:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.50,0:18:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她剛才喝的咖啡裡有安眠藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.61,0:18:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小蘭怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.28,0:18:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔明明打開了這個微波爐的門的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.18,0:18:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是熱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.68,0:18:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.88,0:19:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.38,0:19:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭也被攻擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.39,0:19:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她是被下了安眠藥才睡著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.59,0:19:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安眠藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.89,0:19:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我們不是也喝了咖啡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.40,0:19:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許就在那個裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得剛才到廚房泡咖啡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.50,0:19:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是小蘭跟米嬸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我怎麼會做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.31,0:19:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳剛才跟我一起在樹林裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.88,0:19:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以攻擊小蘭的犯人不可能是妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.68,0:19:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個兇手為什麼要攻擊偶然在這的小蘭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.58,0:19:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就有可能是無差別殺人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.50,0:19:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停電的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.60,0:19:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆不是和小蘭姐姐一起待在這個房間裡的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.80,0:19:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候有沒有什麼奇怪的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.00,0:19:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.20,0:19:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正覺得好像有股暖風吹來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.00,0:19:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈就在這個時候一下子熄掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.61,0:19:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.98,0:20:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是空調
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二點三十分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.58,0:20:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是斷電的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.30,0:20:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有房間裡的空調遙控器的時間都一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.49,0:20:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都被設定在十二點三十分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.60,0:20:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.90,0:20:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來兇手是利用這樣的方法來製造黑暗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.10,0:20:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個兇手果然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.80,0:20:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這棟房子裡面的某個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.71,0:20:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.41,0:20:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能單獨留在房間裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.68,0:20:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 三船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.18,0:20:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說在已經四點多鐘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.58,0:20:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要再有三個小時就有車來接我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.38,0:20:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.58,0:20:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個兇手說不定就在我們中間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.29,0:20:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我怎麼跟他在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.89,0:20:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我也回房休息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.19,0:20:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大家待在一起不是比較安全嗎？
